RETENTIONS MORE COMMENSURATE WITH THE SIZE OF THE RESPECTIVE LOCAL BALANCE

SHEET. THE COMPANY CONDUCTS AN ONGOING REVIEW OF ITS RISK AND CATASTROPHE

COVERAGES AND MAKES CHANGES AS IT DEEMS APPROPRIATE.

