COMPANY ALSO OWNS OTHER REAL PROPERTY, WHICH INCLUDES OFFICE BUILDINGS IN DENVER,

COLORADO, FALL RIVER, MASSACHUSETTS AND IRVING, TEXAS, AND A DATA CENTER

LOCATED IN NORCROSS, GEORGIA. IN JANUARY 2007, THE COMPANY ACQUIRED A

BUILDING AND ADJACENT LAND IN WINDSOR, CONNECTICUT. THE COMPANY LEASES 196

FIELD AND CLAIM OFFICES TOTALING APPROXIMATELY 5.1 MILLION SQUARE FEET

THROUGHOUT THE UNITED STATES UNDER LEASES OR SUBLEASES WITH THIRD PARTIES.

THE COMPANY OWNS A

BUILDING IN LONDON, ENGLAND, WHICH HOUSES A PORTION OF ITS OPERATIONS IN THE

UNITED KINGDOM.

55

