HISTORICALLY, THE ONE-YEAR CHANGE IN THE RESERVE

ESTIMATE FOR THIS PRODUCT LINE OVER THE LAST NINE YEARS HAS VARIED FROM -7%

TO +9% (AVERAGING +1%) FOR THE COMPANY AND -1% TO +9% (AVERAGING +2%) FOR

THE INDUSTRY OVERALL. THE COMPANYS YEAR-TO-YEAR CHANGES ARE DRIVEN BY AND ARE

