THEREOF, THAT COULD CHANGE AND, THUS, AFFECT THE REQUIRED PERSONAL AUTOMOBILE

RESERVES (BEYOND THOSE INCLUDED IN THE GENERAL DISCUSSION SECTION) INCLUDE.

