PRICES OR DEALER QUOTES, OR IF QUOTED MARKET PRICES OR DEALER QUOTES ARE NOT

AVAILABLE, DISCOUNTED EXPECTED CASH FLOWS USING MARKET RATES COMMENSURATE WITH

THE CREDIT QUALITY AND MATURITY OF THE INVESTMENT. EQUITY SECURITIES ARE VALUED

BASED ON QUOTED MARKET PRICES.

