ZERO

COUPON CONVERTIBLE NOTES

THE ZERO COUPON CONVERTIBLE NOTES

MATURE IN 2009, BUT ARE REDEEMABLE AT THE OPTION OF THE COMPANY FOR AN AMOUNT

